s: Basic knowledge of Photoshop or Sketch is required.
Symbol is advanced web-design system based on Sketch nested symbols. There are not only the components but also the logic, the atomic structure.
We prepared a short video to show you how Symbol works.
No other way to create your own Design System
You can easily change just one symbol to create your own design style super fast.
We have prepared a short sneak peek video to grab your attention.
Elements / Values / Input Fields / Paragraph / Text Middle
Early stage company? Eligible applicants get all of our products for just $88 a year.
Elements / Values / Buttons / Paragraph / Middle & Right Icon
Elements / Values / Input Fields / Label / Text Middle
We planing to grow Symbol and made it best Sketch tool ever
Now we working on premade blocks based on Symbold Design Sytem
Difficult to Create, Easy to Use
Change just one color in the pallete and all compnents will be repainted
Elements / Values / Buttons / Paragraph / Middle Right Primary
All components based on atomic structure and works together
Create any web-page design superfast using Symbol Library
We created most simple and beautiful design ever
Build responsive, mobile-first projects on the web
You can adjust each component as you wish. Symbol Design System has lots of Nested Symbols that help you to create web-sites much faster.
Design System has an elaborate system of styles. You can control every single detail: starting with the background color of Navigation bar and ending with the size of the splitter in Elements.
All Instance Symbols are linked with their Elements. A change in one of them will be automatically applied to the others, which ensures the consistency of the whole design.
We offer a 50% discount on all our products for students.
